text: Unions provide millions of Americans with a path to the middle class by increasing income & the economic security of families. As #SCOTUS hears the #Janus case, I commit to protecting the freedom of American workers to join together for their collective bargaining rights.

A bipartisan solution to protect #Dreamers & grant them the pathway to citizenship they've earned was on the table. It failed b/c GOP leadership voted instead to continue enabling @realDonaldTrump's xenophobic agenda. To Dreamers: This isn't it. I will not stop fighting for you.

#ParklandShooting is the 18th school shooting just this year - & it's only February. No, we can't stop every shooting, but there are commonsense steps Congress can take to prevent the slaughtering of children & these senseless mass murders. Congress just needs to step up & do it.

Dreamers are American in every way but paperwork. They pledge allegiance to our flag and the only anthem they know is the Star-Spangled Banner. The time is now to pass legislation to #ProtectDreamers.
This week, we have the opportunity to help #Dreamers. To our friends across the aisle - we say work with us in good faith to provide a permanent solution for these young people. #ProtectDreamers

We've been telling #Dreamers to sit back & be patient for nearly two decades. When #DACA went into effect, we told them that if they gave the gov't their personal info & paid an annual fee, they would be safe. Dreamers have earned a pathway to citizenship. It's time they got it.

I hope the bipartisan spirit w/ the budget deal will carry over to our efforts to put #Dreamers on a pathway to citizenship. While this agreement invests in many of our domestic priorities, I remain committed to ensure funding that will help prevent & combat wildfires in the West

Tonight, the GOP tried to pass a law regulating women's reproductive decisions. Abortions after 20 wks are rare & often occur under extremely complex, difficult circumstances. I was proud to vote against this & will always oppose any bill that restricts a woman's right to choose.

My Catholic faith teaches me that ignorance is not a virtue & that hate is not gospel, unless you're in the Trump Admin. Gov. Brownback is an excellent example of this Admin's callous disregard for basic human rights abroad & at home. I voted no on his nomination today.

.@realDonaldTrump & @SenateMajLdr have made promises to #Dreamers - and they've both failed to keep their word. Time and again.

We need to hold their feet to the fire. We need to keep the pressure on them to pass the #DreamActNow. But we need your voices to get it done.

As of today, 17,036 #DREAMers have lost their #DACA protection - now at risk of deportation, being torn from their families, & the only place they call home. 122 more lose their protection everyday Congress fails to act. We must keep the pressure on the GOP & pass #DreamActNow.

We have less than three weeks to hold @realDonaldTrump @SenateMajLdr's feet to the fire on promises made to protect #Dreamers. Join me in holding them accountable. Call, tweet, email your Reps & tell them to fight for #DreamActNow! 800,000 young lives are hanging in the balance.

.@realDonaldTrump created a crisis when he ended #DACA. Now, thousands of #Dreamers have lost their status, their jobs, & living in fear of deportation. Pitting Americans against one another is no way to govern. I voted no on cloture b/c Dreamers cannot wait. We must act now.

On year two, @realDonaldTrump has chosen to continue his chaotic presidency with a government shutdown. The #TrumpShutdown was completely avoidable and unnecessary. Once again, @POTUS has chosen chaos over consensus. He could end this by leading & coming to the negotiating table.

Every Member of Congress must come together & work to find a solution to end #TrumpShutdown. I will not go home & will not take a salary for as long as Nevadans - & this country - are being impacted by @realDonaldTrump's irresponsible choice to shut down the government.

.@SenateMajLdr had a year to act on a long-term spending bill. He failed to deliver & allowed Trump to threaten futures of #Dreamers. There are bipartisan solutions for all the challenges we're facing. @SenateMajLdr & Trump need to stop blocking Senate from acting on them.

The Senate is now in session, & Dems continue to be ready to negotiate a bipartisan deal & get it across the finish line to avert a #TrumpShutdown. @realDonaldTrump when will you let the GOP know what you'll agree to? The clock is ticking. We need leadership.

GOP controls the House, the Senate, & the WH. We have had four short-term spending bills in the last five months. We have just hours before the gov't shuts down - we need to get to work & govern like the American people sent us here to do. They deserve better. #TrumpShutdown

Trump rescinded #DACA unleashing fear in the hearts of 800k #Dreamers. GOP then refused to fund #CHIP, which 9 million children rely on for care. Now, the GOP is holding both hostage & forcing Dems to pick which to save in order to keep the gov't open. This crisis is on the GOP.

The people of NV didn't send me to DC to become part of the problem. They sent me here to get things done. We need to keep the gov't open, ensure 9 million kids have care through #CHIP, & protect 800,000 #Dreamers from deportation. Ds & Rs need to work together to get this done

With less than 48 hours from a gov't shutdown, we have a POTUS spending his time creating "Fake News Awards." We need a leader who will come to the table & work in good faith with democrats to do what we're elected to do: Help make the American people's lives better, not worse.

In honor of Dr. Martin Luther King Jr., free admission will be offered @DeathValleyNPS @GreatBasinNPS @lakemeadnps. A great way to get outdoors enjoying our precious public lands in NV and reflect on the legacy of #MLK.

122 more #Dreamers will lose their #DACA protection today, in addition to the more than 15,000 young people who've already lost theirs since this #FailingPresident's heartless decision to rescind it. The clock is ticking and too many lives are hanging in the balance #DreamActNow

On #HumanTraffickingAwarenessDay, I reaffirm my commitment in fighting to ensure the victims of this heinous crime have the resources and tools they need to regain their voice and get their life back. Part of that commitment is fighting to ensure Congress passes the #SESTA Act.

#SESTA Act, which I'm a co-sponsor of, would give state law enforcement officials the power to take action against individuals or businesses that violate federal sex trafficking laws. Congress must pass this bill to help ensure justice for victims. #HumanTraffickingAwarenessDay
RT if you stand with #Dreamers and want the GOP to stop the cruel games & pass the #DreamActNow.

#Dreamers are our nation’s veterans, teachers, engineers, business owners & future leaders. Why we wouldn't we want them in our country's future? Deporting them robs our communities of their contributions & betrays America’s immigrant heritage. @SenateGOP pass the #DreamActNow

Ending #TPS for Salvadorans in America is devastating for businesses & state economies. From the @USChamber & @NAHBhome, industry leaders agree we need these hardworking contributors. Congress must act & pass legislation to #SaveTPS

.@realDonaldTrump just ended #TPS for Salvadorans in America, marking the fourth termination of TPS in four months. This is an attack on families and essential workers who love and contribute to our communities. Congress must step up and step in to protect them. #SaveTPS

.@AjitPaiFCC's #NetNeutrality decision destroys the principle of a truly #FreeandOpenInternet. @SenMarkey's CRA, which I've co-sponsored, is crucial to overturning this reckless decision made w/out adequate consumer protections for all who depend on access to quality broadband.

Do you support #NetNeutrality? Do you believe a #FreeandOpenInternet should be accessible to all? 

RT to stand with me, @SenMarkey, & @SenateDems as we push for a vote to #savetheinternet!

.@AjitPaiFCC action to rescind #NetNeutrality rules ends a truly free and open internet as we know it. We must fight. I’m proud to stand for Nevadan’s access to quality broadband, it’s a necessity. That's why I’m co-sponsoring @SenMarkey's CRA that stops Pai's reckless action.

The Senate has a laundry list of issues to address before the government’s short-term funding expires in 2 weeks. We must work to pass the Dream Act, reauthorize CHIP, & stabilize our healthcare system. With your help, we can get this done. Speak out & call your representatives!

122 more Dreamers lost their DACA today, in addition to the more than 14,000 who already lost DACA since September. Time’s running out for these young men and women. Congress must pass the #DreamActNow.

Nevada’s marijuana industry is a boon to our economy: it supports nearly 300 small businesses and currently employs more than 6,700 Nevadans. AG Sessions’ decision to ignore states’ rights will create uncertainty and could cost Nevada millions in economic revenue.

Nevada voters made it clear that the state should be able to enforce its marijuana laws without federal interference. We must respect the will of states while ensuring prosecutorial resources are used effectively.
Wishing all a fun and safe New Year's Eve celebration tonight! Here's to a happy and healthful 2018!
On the first day of the holiday, wishing all those that are celebrating this week a very Happy Kwanzaa!

800,000 #Dreamers don’t want special treatment. They want the chance to continue contributing to our communities without the fear of deportation, and being torn apart from their families, looming over their heads.

The GOP must take up & pass the #DreamActNow #AmericanDreamer

This is a watershed moment. People will ask, where were you when Dreamers lives were hanging in the balance? It's time we pass the #DreamActNow #AmericanDreamer

Trump’s decision to deport #DREAMers is not guided by sound policy, but by xenophobia & myths. Deporting them robs our communities of their contributions and betrays America’s immigrant heritage. We must put partisanship aside and pass the #DreamActNow before the end of the year.

Dreamers are our nation’s teachers, engineers, leaders, business owners, future leaders and so much more; they are our neighbors and our friends. We must protect them from deportation by passing the #DreamActNow #AmericanDREAMer

#DoddFrankRollback weakens stress tests for all large banks – banks that together took $239B in taxpayer bailouts last time around. We cannot afford to gamble another nearly $240B of hardworking Americans' tax dollars on this bill.

Who's helped by #DoddFrankRollback?
-Big Banks.

Who's NOT helped by #DoddFrankRollback?
-Americans burdened with student loan debt. 
-Homeowners who are still underwater. 
-Workers who haven't had a raise in years.

Community banks provide critical services to customers, homeowners & #smallbiz. We must support efforts to help them. But we cannot roll back accountability measures on the largest banks with nothing to help hardworking people who have the most to lose. #DoddFrankRollback

#DoddFrankRollback puts taxpayers at risk of another bank bailout and puts homeowners at risk of the same traps that led to the foreclosure crisis – where NV felt it worst - all while doing virtually nothing for hardworking Americans.

#MonumentsForAll gives us the fortune to experience & explore. Protecting our national monuments is vital, so generations to come can enjoy. They're a source of economic revenue - generating over $59 billion annually - and gives a needed boost to our rural communities' economy.
Early this morning, Republicans forced their #GOPTaxScam through to final passage - all to deliver an early Xmas gift to top 1% & big corps.

#GOPTaxScam gives tax breaks to top 1% under the false promise that America's working families - someday - will be better off because big corporations & investors will do something better with the money than working families.

The GOP delayed their #GOPTaxScam votes until tomorrow. They are now rewriting it as we speak, behind closed doors...again. We need to be helping American families, not big corps. If there were ever a time to make your voices heard, it's now! Call your reps! Time to #KillTheBill

#GOPTaxScam is smoke & mirrors. While the GOP claims it will help hardworking middle-class families, the fact is they will see their taxes go up over a decade. All to give the top 1% & big corps - like Big Oil & Big Banks - permanent tax giveaways to ship American jobs overseas.

The party of "fiscal responsibility" is on the cusp of passing their #GOPTaxScam in Senate. Their bill explodes the deficit by over $1 trillion to give a Christmas bonus to Wall Street, big corps, & top 1%.  

Our future is on the line! Call & tweet to tell your rep to vote NO!

Paul & I are saddened by the passing of our friend, Joe Crowley. Joe dedicated his life to education as a professor & the longest-serving president @unevadareno. I'm infinitely grateful for his support throughout the years. My deepest condolences to Joe's wife, Joy, & his family.

#DREAMers deserve peace of mind before the end of the year, and especially during the holiday season. RT to urge the GOP to bring the #DREAMAct to the floor to #ProtectDREAMers & keep families from being ripped apart!

Republicans, if you support #DREAMers, why not bring the #DREAMAct to the floor for an up-or-down vote? 

Congress must act before the end of the year. It's past time to bring the Dream Act to the floor to #ProtectDreamers!

This, all in the name of giving big corporations & wealthiest tax breaks. Completely outrageous

#GOPTaxScam gives poor & middle-class American families temporary tax relief while handing big corporations, who do not need it, a permanent tax cut. 

Rewarding the wealthiest - who have long exploited loopholes in our tax code to avoid paying their fair share - is plain wrong.

#GOPTaxScam gives the poor & middle-class American families temporary tax relief while handing big corporations, who do not need it, a permanent tax cut. Rewarding the wealthiest that have long exploited loopholes in our tax code to avoid paying their fair share is plain wrong.

How could the #GOPTaxScam help you and your family when their proposal was designed to help the wealthy and America's biggest corporations? 

Tell the GOP to go back to the drawing board and work across the aisle to give meaningful relief to hardworking American families.

I am a proud cosponsor of the Paycheck Fairness Act! It is unconscionable that women are not paid equally for their work. #LatinaEqualPay
RT & spread the word: 80¢ doesn’t tell the whole story. Latinas are paid just 54¢ for every $1 paid to their male colleagues #LatinaEqualPay
My two-cents on the $.54 #wagegap facing Latinas: It’s outrageous & we must push for #LatinaEqualPay by passing the Paycheck Fairness Act!
Over 3m households are headed by Latinas & 40% of those households live below the poverty line. It's time to make #LatinaEqualPay a reality.
Latinas have to work 306 extra days to earn what their male colleagues make in a year - more than any female minority group. #LatinaEqualPay
What does it mean to #StandWithWorkers? It means we'll fight for unions and the middle class - not for corporate special interests.
Janus v. @AFSCME is yet another attempt to chip away at workers’ power in the workplace. Today and every day, we must #StandWithWorkers.
The special interests behind Janus v. @AFSCME want to make the wealthy wealthier at the expense of American workers. I #StandWithWorkers.
Janus v @AFSCME is an attack on workers' freedom to advocate for themselves. We can't let corporate special interests win #StandWithWorkers
To support US jobs, we need to support #EXIM. We must confirm a leader who believes in power of American workers. Scott Garrett's not it.

Big companies are trying to use fine print to silence Nevadans. We must protect consumers, students, & our servicemembers' access to justice
We can't let these big companies off the hook! The @CFPB's rule gives Main Street a fighting chance against the Big Banks & seek justice.
Since @Equifax breach of 143 million Americans' info, I've received nearly 4 dozen letters from Nevadans seeking justice.
With at least 54,000 @WellsFargo fake accounts created in Nevada, it's more important than ever that consumers have protections from @CFPB.
When we let Nevadans have their day in court, it puts another cop on the beat to ensure Big Banks can’t gouge borrowers w/ tricks & traps.
Whether it's fake accounts from @WellsFargo or @Equifax data breach, consumers need access to justice system & have their day in court.
The @CFPB issued a simple, straightforward rule that safeguards the right of every single American consumer to hold Big Banks accountable.
In its short life, the @CFPB has returned $12 billion to 29 million consumers. In NV, the CFPB has worked to resolve about 14,600 cases.
As NV's AG, I took on the Big Banks that preyed upon NV families, bringing back $1.9 billion to NV. Now, @CFPB looks out for consumers.
Fraud shouldn't be kept secret like in @WellsFargo scandal - American people need @CFPB rule so companies don't take advantage of consumers.
.@CFPB’s rule banning forced arbitration guarantees consumers their day in court to hold the worst companies accountable.
Now that @SenateGOP has abandon efforts to rip care away from 32 million, it's critical we work together to fix what needs fixing in #ACA.
